title: Free agency preview
itunes:title: Free agency preview
description:
A room with some heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Chris Wesseling -- discuss the latest news around the NFL including updates on Adrian Peterson and the Browns' new logo. Plus, the guys list which big name players are strong candidates to be released and other potentially surprising free agents.
